rcairo
------------------------------------------
Ruby bindings for the cairo graphics engine.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.19-4
  libcairo2-1.0.2-1
  ruby-1.8.4-1

Build requirements:
  cygwin-1.5.19-4
  binutils-20050610-1
  cygport-0.1.5-1
  gcc-core-3.4.4-1
  make-3.80-1
  ruby-1.8.4-1
  cairo-1.0.2-1

Canonical website:
  http://cairographics.org/

Canonical download:
  http://cairographics.org/releases/

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  unpack rcairo-1.0.0-X-src.tar.bz2
    if you use setup to install this src package, it will be
	 unpacked under /usr/src automatically
  cd /usr/src
  ./rcairo-1.0.0-X.sh all

This will create:
  /usr/src/rcairo-1.0.0-X-src.tar.bz2
  /usr/src/rcairo-1.0.0-X.tar.bz2

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

  /usr/lib/ruby/site_ruby/1.8/cairo.rb
  /usr/lib/ruby/site_ruby/1.8/i386-cygwin/cairo.so
  /usr/lib/ruby/site_ruby/1.8/i386-cygwin/libruby-cairo.a
  /usr/lib/ruby/site_ruby/1.8/i386-cygwin/rb_cairo.h
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/rcairo-1.0.0.README
  /usr/share/doc/rcairo-1.0.0/AUTHORS
  /usr/share/doc/rcairo-1.0.0/COPYING
  /usr/share/doc/rcairo-1.0.0/ChangeLog
  /usr/share/doc/rcairo-1.0.0/GPL
  /usr/share/doc/rcairo-1.0.0/NEWS
  /usr/share/doc/rcairo-1.0.0/README

------------------

Port Notes:

